Comment.val: /*Service to report differences between positions in the Reynders register and the current positioins. Servicename is 'DiffReynRegisterVsPosReprt' because 'JMS Verwerken Verzoeken' cuts off 'report' of the servicename, so 'DiffReynRegisterVsPosReport' won't work! The service will be called by the Job Monitor when all differences are determined.*/

SQL_STMT_U.val: select r.response "RESPONSE" from responsesperjob r where r.job_id=~1 --Order by the Symbol of the instrumentkey: order by xmlquery( 'declare namespace drprs="http://www.topicus.nl/epp/tap/diffreynregvsposperfund/response"; //drprs:diffReynRegVsPosPerFundResponse/instrument/instrumentKey/symbol/text()' passing xmltype.createxml(r.response) returning content).getStringVal()

Text.valUnicode: VERSCHIL REYNDERS TAX REGISTER VS ACTUELE POSITIES
